== Genealogy == According to the ''Nihon Shoki,'' Tamichi was the son of {{ill|Ōaratabe no Mikoto|ja|大荒田別命|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōaratabe no Mikoto|qq=}} and the younger brother of {{ill|Takehase|ja|竹葉瀬|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takehase|qq=}}.
